{
  "stem": "166.2",
  "chunk_idx": 6,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 11.3,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 54,
      "text": "It would take maybe three hours until I got one spoon.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 55,
      "text": "As soon as I gave a sip, I collapsed.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 56,
      "text": "And my friend nearby, he start hitting me so hard that, I don't know-- I opened my eyes again.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 57,
      "text": "He don't live anymore.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 58,
      "text": "He died.",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 59,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] Then, three days later, we march-- walked out from this barrack and appel again.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 60,
      "text": "And we stay, and we stay, and we stay.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 61,
      "text": "And finally, they hung up-- maybe 10 people they hang.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 62,
      "text": "And they-- they didn't give us any reason for what.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 63,
      "text": "They gave us a ration of bread, and they put us on trains.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 64,
      "text": "And we were sent to Buchenwald.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 65,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 5 SECONDS] We were riding to Buchenwald the whole week on the trains.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 66,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 5 SECONDS] In open trains-- no water.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 67,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] When-- no water, no food.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 68,
      "text": "For a whole week, we were staying like this when it was snowing so the snow should come in in your mouth for a little bit of water.",
      "word_count": 28
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 69,
      "text": "The trains-- they were rolling slow, and they stopped.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 70,
      "text": "And they rolled slow, and they stopped again.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 71,
      "text": "Any people-- they ask for something, help, they just walked by.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 72,
      "text": "Nothing.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 73,
      "text": "One guy says to the other, please, give me a little bit of urine, because I don't have anymore to drink.",
      "word_count": 21
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 74,
      "text": "I'm dying for thirst.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 75,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 5 SECONDS] We finally came in to Buchenwald in the middle of the night.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 76,
      "text": "We came into Weimar.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 77,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] Weimar was the town before we had to march into Buchenwald.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 78,
      "text": "In the middle of the night, there was no room to go into camp-- the camp.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 79,
      "text": "We had to wait on the station.",
      "word_count": 7
    }
  ],
